Install the following: 
Create Github account repo, download emulator layer of git on windows: https://git-scm.com/downloads Branch – discreate pathway 
Visual studio code - https://code.visualstudio.com/download 
Node js – https://nodejs.org/en/ check in cmd or terminal 
 
Create a directory from terminal in documents as dev. Clone git directory in this folder 
Git clone https://github.com/alviranarshidani/MDEV1001MobileDataManagement 
 
Open dev in vscode 
 
npm – package manager for nodejs 
>npm init 
>Alviras-MacBook-Dev:MDEV1001MobileDataManagement alviranarshidani$ npm install—save RepoName typescript @types/node 
 
Exclude dependencies in project – create .gitignore file write node_modules and save and stage and commit changes 
 
Add index.js 
To run on terminal: Alviras-MacBook-Pro:MDEV1001MobileDataManagement alviranarshidani$ node index 
 
Delete index.js  
 
Create tsconfig.json 
Keep watch: ./node_modules/.bin/tsc 
Index.ts 
 
Run  
node index 
